    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## How to Use This Workflow\n\n**1. Send PDF via POST request:**\n```bash\ncurl -X POST https://your-n8n-instance/webhook/pdf-upload \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"pdfFile\": \"base64-encoded-pdf-data\",\n    \"filename\": \"document.pdf\"\n  }'\n```\n\n**2. Response format:**\n- `success`: Boolean indicating success\n- `extractedText`: Full text content\n- `sections`: Array of structured sections\n- `metadata`: File statistics and info\n\n**3. Error handling:**\n- Validation errors return 400 status\n- Processing errors return detailed error info",
        "height": 408,
